# Scope Refinement & Solution Shaping

Challenge for:
1. Missing exception paths and approval/delegation logic
2. Missing audit, compliance, and reporting requirements
3. Missing role boundaries and collaboration touchpoints
4. Teams/M365 interactions, Power Automate flows, Microsoft Copilot Studio agent placement
5. Time-based or recurring work
6. Organizational outputs (documents, summaries, presentations)

Do NOT move to technical implementation until the solution boundary is stable.

